    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onConnectedAndCompatible()
      This callback is hit after getInstance() is called if the SDK was able to authenticate and if the device is compatible with the SDK.
      void onConnectedAndIncompatible()
      This callback is hit after getInstance() is called if the SDK was able to authenticate but the device is not compatible with the SDK.
      void onConnectionFailed()
      This callback is hit after getInstance() is called if the SDK was not able to authenticate.
